# API Keys Configuration for Python Scripts
# Copy this file to .env.scripts and add your actual API keys
# NEVER commit .env.scripts to version control (it's in .gitignore)

# Anthropic API Key (for Claude)
# Get from: https://console.anthropic.com/settings/keys
ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=your_anthropic_api_key_here

# OpenAI API Key (if using GPT models)
# Get from: https://platform.openai.com/api-keys
OPENAI_API_KEY=your_openai_api_key_here

# Security Notes:
# - Name this file .env.scripts (not .env) to prevent Claude Code auto-loading
# - Keep this file LOCAL only
# - NEVER export API key to .zshrc or .bashrc
# - NEVER commit .env.scripts to git
# - Python scripts load with: load_dotenv('.env.scripts')
# - Claude Code uses your Pro subscription (separate billing)
